# ============================================================================
# INSTRUCTIONS FOR VERCEL:
# ============================================================================
# 1. Go to: https://vercel.com/dashboard
# 2. Select your project (or create new)
# 3. Navigate to: Settings → Environment Variables
# 4. For each variable above:
#    - Click "Add New"
#    - Variable Name: (copy from above, e.g., DATABASE_BACKEND)
#    - Value: (copy value from above)
#    - Environment: Select "Production", "Preview", "Development" (or all)
#    - Click "Save"
# 5. After adding all variables, trigger a new deployment
#
# IMPORTANT NOTES:
# - Variables starting with NEXT_PUBLIC_ are exposed to the browser
# - SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY should NOT have NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix
# - Update NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL and NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL after deployment
# - Commented variables (starting with #) are optional
# ============================================================================

